@@TJvListView.OnAutoSort
Description:
This event is called when the user clicks a column and if the SortOnClick property is set to true. This event is used to tell to the component the type of data of a column. if this event is not Assigned, the data type is auto detected. Auto detection try to extract a number in the beginning of the text, if there is no number, its is just a basic string comparison (Date is not supported in autodect mode)

