@@TJvSortMethod
Description:
This is the enumeration of the Sort methods. if you don't know the type of data in the column, just put smAutomatic, but it's a lot more slower !.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TOnSortMethod
Description:
This is the event used in the TJvListview when sorting a column. Column is the index of the column (0 is for the first one (caption), 1 is for the first subitem, etc...). The result of the function is the type of data in the column.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TProgress
Description:
This is the event fired when loading/saving data from a control. 
Progression is the current progression (ex : 1). 
Total is the total number of iterations (ex : 100).

